Powell←{
    a b c d←⍵ ⋄ r5 r10←5 10*÷2 ⋄ y←(a+10×b)(r5×c-d)(×⍨b-2×c)(r10××⍨a-d)
    y[1 10 0 0 ⋄ 0 0 r5(-r5) ⋄ 0(2×b-2×c)(¯4×b-2×c)0 ⋄ (2×r10×a-d)0 0(-2×r10×a-d)]
}
PowellHessian←{
    r j←Powell ⍵
    h←(⍉j)+.×j
    r10←10*÷2
    h3←4 4⍴0 0 0 0 0 2 ¯4 0 0 ¯4 8 0 0 0 0 0
    h4←4 4⍴(2×r10)0 0(-2×r10)0 0 0 0 0 0 0 0(-2×r10)0 0(2×r10)
    h+(r[3]×h3)+(r[4]×h4)
}
